\/2MNRLHVKTrswxwGMuUO-4o31mDR4RPxCwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_PBqUjkt4zL_LvshK.png","title":"Italian Wedding Soup","publishedAt":"2018-08-24T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"27 g","fat":"13 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"28 g","calories":"1393 kJ \/ 333 kcal"},"usefulItems":"parchment paper, fine mesh sieve","hintsAndTricks":["To cut parchment to fit Varoma: tear off a piece of parchment paper wide enough to cover Varoma tray. Place Varoma tray on top of parchment and cut around the tray to form an oval shape. Ensure parchment does not cover side vents to allow circulation of steam."],"basicInfo":["easy","35m","1h 15m","6 portions"]}